library(tidyverse)
library(papaja)
library(psych)
library(apaTables)
library(ggpubr)
library(readr)
library(sjPlot)
X2015 <- read_csv("2015.csv")
View(X2015)

df<-na.omit(X2015)
View(df)
summary <- df %>%
describe() %>%
select(mean, sd, median, min, max)
apa_table(
summary,
caption = "Summary of World Happiness Index",)

  geom_point()+
  geom_smooth(method="lm")
